article.headline: Siena 71, Iona 53
article.story: NEW ROCHELLE, N.Y. (AP) -- Kenny Hasbrouck scored 20 points to help Siena beat Iona 71-53 on Friday night in the Gaels' first game since they beat Rider for their lone victory of the season. Edwin Ubiles added 16 points and nine rebounds for Siena (14-10, 9-5 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). De'Shaune Griffin led Iona (1-23, 1-13) with 16 points, and Justin Marshall had 15.
